title: Mets beat Cubs for NL pennant, head to World Series!
text: Blogs Mets beat Cubs for NL pennant, head to World Series! Ya Gotta Believe! The Mets, somehow, some way, have made it to the World Series! And they partied like they did after sweeping the Cubs.   10/22/2015 1:32:59 METS WIN THE PENNANT! HEADING TO WORLD SERIES! Jeurys Familia drops to his knees a la Jesse Orosco after he gets the final out to finish off the Cubs in the NLCS and give the Mets their first World Series appearance in nine years. 1 of 24
